              <span id="reviewTextContainer1820340477" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15860682249014887827">When I finished the last page of this book, I threw it across the room. I thought people only did that in anecdotes. Ironically enough, this book has turned me into a moderately implausible anecdote.<br/><br/>You should read it. Read all his things. CP is my hero.<br/><br/>(P.S., the blurb is terrible. I assure you, this is not a book about a sad writer boy whose girlfriend left him. Everyone here is better than that.)</span>

